{"tid":1148524,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"（嘈交要自貼身材）健身資訊討論區53","createTime":"2019-05-10T13:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T13:53:30.000Z","uid":8827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"176c85b8cc999913e9347983396335f5a9255d79","tid":1148524,"uid":8827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:50:46.000Z","msg":"一要努力，二要努力，三四五六七都係要努力<br />\n<br />\n講咩都得訓練飲食問題心得資料分享<br />\n<br />\n無乜嘢唔好嘈交，因為嘈交要自貼<br />\n唔好貼自己TG出黎，搵食出返去唔會阻你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n健身係一條漫長既路,無論增肌定減脂肯堅持就會成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aedab1659269d13174d00ec74ddf43fcfed4c35b","tid":1148524,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:51:22.000Z","msg":"53<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c970aea787f7fa95e938a340c2ecf6be2829d325","tid":1148524,"uid":113373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:51:31.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">立法會集會:<br />\n5月11日 星期六 早上8:30 (開會討論修訂逃犯條例)<br />\n<br />\n若不能阻止立法，稍後立法會二讀/三讀時，行動將升級<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人多達46條罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"55b5c7be20fcc9f014a86231414bdeb6b06304f4","tid":1148524,"uid":8827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aedab1659269d13174d00ec74ddf43fcfed4c35b","tid":1148524,"uid":222189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:51:22.000Z","msg":"53<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj